1. **No code before design.** Do not write or propose implementation code (Noun) before the design doc (e.g. `docs/ai/design/feature-{name}.md` or `docs/ai/design/README.md`) has been read and the task's Acceptance Criteria and implementation details are known. If in State B, you must have completed Step 1 (Initialize) before Step 2 (Build).

